efficiency: HIGH
time complexity: O(N * 2^N)
space complexity: O(2^N)
energy implications: MEDIUM
explanation: Uses memoization to avoid recomputation of sub-expressions. Splits the string at every operator, recursively computes all possible results for left and right parts, then combines them. Strength: avoids exponential blow-up via memoization. Weakness: still exponential in worst case due to Catalan number of combinations.

